title: Wednesday Post Show (02-09-22)

description:
Bobby starts the show talking about how his butt is sore. Eddie has a question about if Jake Owen is his friend after his kid’s question their friendship. Bobby talks more about his night hosting the Opry and getting home late and having an awesome dinner. We get into a big discussion about what we like for dinner.
